sequenceDiagram
    participant vLLM as vLLM Servers
    participant Prom as Prometheus/Thanos<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant SatEng as Saturation Engine<br/>(30s polling)
    participant Cache as Decision Cache<br/>(in-memory)
    participant Reconciler as VA Reconciler
    participant Actuator as Actuator<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HPAKEDA as HPA / KEDA
    participant EPP as EPP Pods<br/>HTTPS
    participant SFZEng as Scale-From-Zero Engine<br/>(100ms polling)

    Note over vLLM, Prom: vLLM metrics scraped by Prometheus

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over SatEng, HPAKEDA: Flow 1: Saturation-Based Autoscaling Loop
        SatEng->>Prom: PromQL query (KV cache, queue depth,<br/>tokens, TTFT, ITL)<br/>HTTPS + Bearer Token (SA)
        Prom-->>SatEng: vLLM metrics response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

        alt V2 Token-Based Analyzer
            SatEng->>SatEng: Analyze token capacity<br/>(cache_config_info)
        else V1 Percentage Analyzer
            SatEng->>SatEng: Check KV cache % +<br/>queue thresholds
        else Queueing Model
            SatEng->>SatEng: M/M/1 latency/throughput<br/>prediction
        end

        SatEng->>SatEng: Run Optimizer<br/>(CostAware or GreedyByScore)
        SatEng->>Cache: Write VariantDecision<br/>(Go channel)
        Cache->>Reconciler: Trigger via DecisionTrigger<br/>(GenericEvent channel)

        Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Patch VA status<br/>(desiredReplicas)<br/>HTTPS + SA token
        Reconciler->>Actuator: Emit metrics

        Prom->>Actuator: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTPS 8443/TCP + Bearer Token
        Actuator-->>Prom: wva_desired_replicas,<br/>wva_desired_ratio,<br/>wva_current_replicas

        HPAKEDA->>Prom: Read wva_desired_ratio<br/>HTTPS + SA token
        HPAKEDA->>K8sAPI: Scale Deployment/LWS<br/>HTTPS + SA token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over EPP, SFZEng: Flow 2: Scale-From-Zero Detection
        SFZEng->>EPP: Scrape queue metrics<br/>(inference_extension_flow_control_queue_size)<br/>HTTPS + Bearer Token (EPP token)
        EPP-->>SFZEng: Queue size per model<br/>HTTPS response

        alt Queue size > 0 AND replicas == 0
            SFZEng->>K8sAPI: Scale 0→1 via /scale subresource<br/>HTTPS + SA token
            SFZEng->>Cache: Write scale-from-zero decision<br/>(Go channel)
            Cache->>Reconciler: Trigger reconciliation
        end
    end
